    <item>
      <title>英国高昂的住房成本意味着成年子女在家居住的时间更长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/uk-s-high-housing-costs-mean-adult-children-live-at-home-longer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高昂的住房、儿童保育和学生债务成本，英国的年轻人比他们的前辈要花几年的时间才能达到人生的里程碑，包括离开父母的家和生孩子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/uk-s-high-housing-costs-mean-adult-children-live-at-home-longer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
